    "content": "Finding a 2 BHK flat in Jayanagar under ₹1 Crore is increasingly difficult — but absolutely possible if you know where to look. With prices ranging from ₹13,000-18,000 per sq ft, your budget realistically gets you a 600-750 sq ft apartment in older buildings.\n\n**Best Blocks for Sub-₹1 Crore Buys**\nThe 1st Block, 2nd Block, and pockets of 3rd Block still have older 2 BHK flats in the ₹60-95 Lakh range. Properties like [Asha Kiran Apartment](/?property=2) in Basavanagudi (just adjacent to Jayanagar) currently offer 662 sq ft 2 BHK at ₹60 Lakh. The 3rd East Block's [Vani Apartments](/?property=5) has 2 BHK options around ₹85 Lakh.\n\n**What to Expect**\nAt this budget, you're looking at buildings 20-30 years old with basic amenities. Expect lift, covered parking for one vehicle, and 24/7 security. Most won't have swimming pools or gyms. The trade-off is location — you're walking distance to Metro, parks, top schools, and Sagar/Manipal Hospitals.\n\n**Red Flags to Watch**\nVerify khata, encumbrance certificate, and BBMP property tax receipts before any payment. Older buildings sometimes have unauthorized 4th floors that lack OC. Always insist on seeing the original sale deed chain.\n\n**The Vani Estates Advantage**\nWith 35+ years operating in Jayanagar, we know exactly which buildings are well-maintained and which ones to avoid. Contact us before you finalize anything.",
